text: Xavier Gomez (born November 21, 1994) is an American soccer player who currently plays for Union Omaha in USL League One. He is a native of Des Plaines, IL and graduated from Maine West High School. He was selected No. 41 overall (second round) by Minnesota United FC in the 2018 MLS SuperDraft.
